        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "In the QuickStart on the \"Create a Model and Database Table\" page in the app.ini code sample the following line incorrectly references the SQLite database file:\n\ndatabase.params.dbname = APPLICATION_PATH \"\/..\/data\/db\/guestbook.db\"\n\nI believe it should be:\n\ndatabase.params.dbname = APPLICATION_PATH \"\/data\/db\/guestbook.db\"\n\nAlso, the paragraph following the bootstrap.php code sample should also be modified if the database is actually located in the \/application\/data\/db\/ directory and not the application\/data\/ directory as the page states.\n\n"
        },
